casebody.data:
Michael L. CUPPS, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
S & J TUBE, INC., Defendant-Appellee. No. 17-1922 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Michael Cupps appeals the district court's grant of the defendant's motion for summary judgment. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
